<zk xmlns:n="http://www.zkoss.org/2005/zk/native">
	<n:h2>[ 1797701 ] Slider tooltip text customization</n:h2>
	<n:ol>
		<n:li>drag the slider, it will show scrolling message, then click the button and drag again, the message should change.</n:li>
	</n:ol>
	<slider id="sld" slidingtext="Here is a position : {0}"/>
	<button label="change" onClick='sld.slidingtext = "position {0} is here " '/>
</zk>
